{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"situational-15000","unitId":"scene-372","title":"山区山地","sectionId":"chapter-16","sectionTitle":"天文地理有规律","pageStart":1814,"pageEnd":1818,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":6,"duplicateEntryCount":25,"pages":[{"number":1814,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"372 山区山地"},{"type":"section","text":"Step1 场景词"},{"type":"entry","text":"hilly area 山地","headword":"hilly area"},{"type":"entry","text":"barren mountain 荒山","headword":"barren mountain"}]},{"number":1815,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"mountain meadow soil 山地草甸土","headword":"mountain meadow soil"},{"type":"entry","text":"muck soil 黑泥土","headword":"muck soil"}]},{"number":1816,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"mountain landscape 山地景观","headword":"mountain landscape"}]},{"number":1817,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"vastness [ˈvɑːstnəs]","headword":"vastness"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.巨大，广大"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"},{"type":"example","text":"A：I want to spend two days in the mountains with friends. The city is"},{"type":"text","text":"too noisy. Do you know Tanzhe Temple? （我和朋友想去山里玩两天。"},{"type":"text","text":"城里太闹腾了。知道潭柘寺吗？）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：I have been there. It is in the middle of the mountains. （我去"},{"type":"text","text":"过，在半山腰上。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：Look at the magnificent view of the mountains. （来看看群山的"},{"type":"text","text":"壮丽景色吧。）"}]},{"number":1818,"blocks":[{"type":"example","text":"B：Wow, it is amazing. （哇，太令人震惊了。）"}]}]}